.SH SEE ALSO
sh(1), execve(2), fork(2), wait(2), fflush(3), getline(3), waitpid(3), isatty(3), sprintf(3), fprintf(3)

.SH NOTES
- The shell does not handle PATH resolution (unless implemented).
.br
- The shell does not support pipes, redirection, or advanced features.
